---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="How CMI Assignment Help Works | CMI Assignment Support"
  description="The simple 5-step process to get expert CMI assignment help from CMI Assignment Support UK."
  slug="/how-it-works/"
  schemas={[]}
  breadcrumb={[{ label: 'How It Works', href: '/how-it-works/' }]}
>
  <article class="prose-page">
    <h1>How CMI Assignment Help Works</h1>
    <p>Getting CMI assignment help starts with a single WhatsApp message. There is no lengthy registration, no upfront payment before a quote, and no delay in connecting you with a writer who knows your level and unit.</p>

    <div class="step-block">
      <div class="step-number">1</div>
      <div>
        <p style="margin:0;font-weight:600">Send your assignment brief on WhatsApp</p>
        <p>Share your unit number, level, word count requirement, deadline, and any specific instructions from your assessor. A screenshot of your assignment task works perfectly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-block">
      <div class="step-number">2</div>
      <div>
        <p style="margin:0;font-weight:600">Receive your quote and timeline confirmation</p>
        <p>We confirm the price, turnaround time, and the writer assigned to your work, usually within a few hours of your message.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-block">
      <div class="step-number">3</div>
      <div>
        <p style="margin:0;font-weight:600">Writer is assigned and work begins</p>
        <p>Your assignment is matched to a writer with direct experience in your CMI level and unit subject. Work starts immediately on confirmation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-block">
      <div class="step-number">4</div>
      <div>
        <p style="margin:0;font-weight:600">Draft delivered with revisions included</p>
        <p>Standard turnaround is 5–7 business days. Express 48-hour turnaround is available for urgent submissions. Your draft is delivered in full, and one round of revisions is included at no additional cost.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-block">
      <div class="step-number">5</div>
      <div>
        <p style="margin:0;font-weight:600">Submission-ready document received</p>
        <p>You receive a complete, formatted assignment document ready to submit through your institution&apos;s portal. All references are formatted to CMI standards.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <div style="flex:1">
        <p style="font-weight:600;margin:0 0 0.25rem">Ready to get started?</p>
        <p style="margin:0;font-size:0.95rem">WhatsApp us now with your unit details for a free quote.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="https://wa.me/[WHATSAPP_NUMBER]" class="whatsapp-inline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        WhatsApp: Free Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
